Also , this myth claims that Confucius was fond of birds , which would explain the name " Mahjong " ( sparrow ) . 
====== 5 ======
However , there is no evidence of Mahjong 's existence prior to the Taiping era in the 19th century which eliminates Confucius as a likely inventor . 
Another theory implies the game was developed from existing Chinese card and domino games sometime around 1850 . 
Many historians believe it was based on a Chinese card game called Mádiào ( &#x99AC ; &#x540A ; ) ( also known as Ma Tiae , lit . 
