====== 7 ======
Wind tiles : East ( &#x6771 ; , d&#x14D ; ng ) , South ( &#x5357 ; , nán ) , West ( &#x897F ; , x&#x12B ; ) , and North ( &#x5317 ; , b&#x11B ; i ) . 
