Flower tiles : The last category and typically optional components to a set of mahjong tiles , often contain artwork on their tiles . 
The suits of the tiles are money-based . 
In ancient China , the copper coins had a square hole in the centre . 
People passed a rope through the holes to tie coins into strings . 
