If the player wins by drawing a tile from a wall during his turn , a special name is given to this type of win in Chinese and Japanese ( Chinese : &#x81EA ; &#x6478 ; , Japanese : &#x30C4 ; &#x30E2 ; ) . 
Variations may also have special nonstandard hands that a player can make ( in this sense , American Mahjong is a variant where only special hands exist ) . 
